OL,3,CMan accused of murder pleads guilty to
OL,4,Ccausing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA former painter and decorator who is
OL,7,Faccused of deliberately driving into a
OL,8,Fgroup of people - killing one of them
OL,9,F- has pleaded guilty to causing death
OL,10,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,12,FMartin Breeze, 57, accepts
OL,13,Fresponsibility for causing Brian
OL,14,FDarby's death on 9 February this year,
OL,15,Fwhen his work van crashed into a group
OL,16,Fof friends who were on a footpath,
OL,17,FTeesside Crown Court has heard.
OL,19,FMr Darby, 60, died instantly in the
OL,20,Fcollision on Myton Way in Ingleby
OL,21,FBarwick.
