OL,3,CMan accused of murder pleads guilty to
OL,4,Ccausing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FThree others were seriously injured
OL,7,Fand one man narrowly escaped harm.
OL,9,FBreeze denies murder and three counts
OL,10,Fof attempted murder - but he has now
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to causing death by
OL,12,Fdangerous driving and three counts of
OL,13,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,14,Fdriving.
OL,16,FHe remains on trial for the murder and
OL,17,Fattempted murder charges.
