OL,3,CMan accused of murder pleads guilty to
OL,4,Ccausing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FIt is the prosecution's case that
OL,7,FMartin Breeze, encouraged from the
OL,8,Fpassenger seat by his son Shaun
OL,9,FBreeze, 29, drove over a grass verge
OL,10,Fand into the group in a revenge attack
OL,11,Fafter he received a panic-stricken
OL,12,Fphone call from his son.
OL,14,FShaun Breeze made a late night phone
OL,15,Fcall to his dad to say that some of
OL,16,Fthe group were chasing after him, on
OL,17,Fhis bike. When he came off his push
OL,18,Fbike, he claims the men continued to
OL,19,Fchase him.
