OL,3,CMan accused of murder pleads guilty to
OL,4,Ccausing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FThe group of friends had left the 3
OL,7,FRivers Bar & Coffee Shop moments
OL,8,Fearlier, and say that Shaun Breeze
OL,9,Fcycled into them, which led to two of
OL,10,Fthem chasing him along the footpath.
OL,12,FMartin Breeze had consumed alcohol and
OL,13,Fcocaine when he set off his White
OL,14,FCitroen Berlingo van to pick up his
OL,15,Fson from outside the nearby Co-op at
OL,16,F11.30pm. The prosecution alleges that
OL,17,FShaun Breeze then pointed out the
OL,18,Fgroup to his dad.
