OL,3,CMan accused of murder pleads guilty to
OL,4,Ccausing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FMinutes later, CCTV captured the van
OL,7,Fveering off Myton Way, and onto the
OL,8,Fadjacent footpath. Brian Darby was
OL,9,Fcarried on the van's bonnet before his
OL,10,Fbody was thrown to the ground. His
OL,11,Fthree friends suffered broken bones in
OL,12,Fthe crash.
OL,14,FIt is alleged that Martin and Shaun
OL,15,FBreeze abandoned the van and walked
OL,16,Fhome. The next morning they falsely
OL,17,Freported the van as stolen and were
OL,18,Flater arrested on suspicion of murder.
