OL,3,CMan accused of murder pleads guilty to
OL,4,Ccausing death by dangerous driving
OL,6,FAs the trial draws to a close, Martin
OL,7,FBreeze pleaded guilty to the lesser
OL,8,Fcharges, when they were formally put
OL,9,Fto him.
OL,11,FMartin Breeze, of Irthing Close and
OL,12,FShaun Breeze, of Owl's Grove in
OL,13,FIngleby Barwick, continue to deny the
OL,14,Fmurder of Brian Darby, and the
OL,15,Fattempted murder of three others.
